cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper focuses on using machine learning techniques to improve control policies for drone racing, which involves perception and navigation tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses the use of unsupervised data and simulations, which suggests a possible fit with cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
